with orders as (
    select * from `dbt-project-24`.`dbt_mesh`.`stg_orders`
),

customers as (
    select * from `dbt-project-24`.`dbt_mesh`.`stg_customers`
),

locations as (
    select * from `dbt-project-24`.`dbt_mesh`.`stg_locations`
),

joined as (
    select
        orders.order_id, 
        orders.location_id,
        orders.customer_id,
        orders.order_total,
        orders.tax_paid,
        orders.ordered_at,
        customers.customer_name,
        locations.location_name,
        locations.tax_rate,
        locations.location_opened_at

    from 
       orders 
        left join customers 
            on orders.customer_id = customers.customer_id
        left join locations 
            on orders.location_id = locations.location_id    
)

with products as (
    select * from `dbt-project-24`.`dbt_mesh`.`stg_products`
),

supplies as (
    select * from `dbt-project-24`.`dbt_mesh`.`stg_supplies`
),

product_supplies_summary as (
    select
        product_id,
        sum(supply_cost) as supply_cost
    from supplies
    group by 1
),

final as (
    select
        products.*,
        product_supplies_summary.supply_cost
    from products
        left join product_supplies_summary 
            on products.product_id = product_supplies_summary.product_id
)
